data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN @ 2.25%! This lovely 1 story home home in Rancho Sienna has been lovingly maintained and is move-in ready, and features 3 bedrooms plus a separate office with French doors off the entryway. No carpeting - tile throughout all living areas, and wood laminate in bedrooms and office. Granite counters in the kitchen with a spacious island and plenty of cabinets and counter space. Rancho Sienna amenities include a community pool and splash pad, 24/7 fitness center, dog park, event lawn, covered pavilion, 100 acres of parkland, basketball courts and miles of hike and bike trails. Zoned to highly rated Liberty Hill ISD schools!
